<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA75">
<l>kāppuṉṉai yuṉṉak kaḻiyu maruviṉaika</l>
<l>ḷāppuṉṉai yuṉṉa vaviḻntoḻiyu – mūppuṉṉaic</l>
<l>cintippārk killai tirumālē niṉṉaṭiyai</l>
<l>vantippār kāṇpar vaḻi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When one considers you as protection, the difficult karmas pass.</l>
<l>When one considers you, the bonds open [and] vanish. For those</l>
<l>who ponder you, there is no old age, Tirumāl. Those who praise</l>
<l>your feet will see the way.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
